<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Zone Restreinte</title>
<style>
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: #0a0a0a;
    color: #00ff41;
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }

  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      repeating-linear-gradient(
        0deg,
        transparent,
        transparent 2px,
        rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.03) 2px,
        rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.03) 4px
      );
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 10;
  }

  .container {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    max-width: 620px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 5;
  }

  .warning-icon {
    font-size: 5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 20px rgba(255, 60, 60, 0.6));
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
    50% { opacity: 0.7; transform: scale(1.05); }
  }

  .code { font-size: 6rem; font-weight: bold; color: #ff3c3c;
    text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255, 60, 60, 0.5); line-height: 1; }

  h1 { font-size: 1.4rem; margin: 1.2rem 0 0.5rem;
    text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 4px; color: #ff3c3c; }

  .classified {
    display: inline-block; padding: 0.3rem 1.2rem; margin: 1rem 0;
    border: 2px solid #ff3c3c; color: #ff3c3c; font-size: 0.9rem;
    letter-spacing: 6px; text-transform: uppercase;
    animation: blink 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes blink {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; } 50% { opacity: 0.4; }
  }

  .message { color: #00cc33; font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 1.5rem 0; }

  .terminal-line { color: #00ff41; font-size: 0.75rem; opacity: 0.6;
    margin: 0.3rem 0; }

  .terminal-line::before { content: '> '; color: #ff3c3c; }

  .grid-bg {
    position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 1;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 40px 40px;
  }

  .corner { position: fixed; width: 60px; height: 60px; z-index: 2; }
  .corner::before, .corner::after {
    content: ''; position: absolute; background: #ff3c3c;
  }
  .tl { top: 20px; left: 20px; }
  .tl::before { width: 30px; height: 2px; top: 0; left: 0; }
  .tl::after  { width: 2px; height: 30px; top: 0; left: 0; }
  .tr { top: 20px; right: 20px; }
  .tr::before { width: 30px; height: 2px; top: 0; right: 0; }
  .tr::after  { width: 2px; height: 30px; top: 0; right: 0; }
  .bl { bottom: 20px; left: 20px; }
  .bl::before { width: 30px; height: 2px; bottom: 0; left: 0; }
  .bl::after  { width: 2px; height: 30px; bottom: 0; left: 0; }
  .br { bottom: 20px; right: 20px; }
  .br::before { width: 30px; height: 2px; bottom: 0; right: 0; }
  .br::after  { width: 2px; height: 30px; bottom: 0; right: 0; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="grid-bg"></div>
  <div class="corner tl"></div>
  <div class="corner tr"></div>
  <div class="corner bl"></div>
  <div class="corner br"></div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="warning-icon">&#9888;</div>
    <div class="code">403</div>
    <h1>Acces non autorise</h1>
    <div class="classified">Classifie</div>
    <div class="message">
      Vous tentez d'acceder a une zone restreinte.<br>
      Ce secteur est sous surveillance permanente.<br>
      Seul le personnel autorise disposant d'un acces<br>
      reseau securise peut penetrer dans cette zone.
    </div>
    <div class="terminal-line">CONNEXION REFUSEE &mdash; PROTOCOLE VPN REQUIS</div>
    <div class="terminal-line">INCIDENT JOURNALISE &mdash; ID: <span id="ts"></span></div>
    <div class="terminal-line">COORDONNEES VISITEUR ENREGISTREES</div>
  </div>
  <script>
    document.getElementById('ts').textContent =
      new Date().toISOString().replace(/[-:T]/g,'').slice(0,14);
  </script>
</body>
</html>
